  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Thinking about the different configuration options of lodestar and the potential for adding many more in the future, it will be useful to allow for full configuration from a file as an additional option.\r\n\r\neg:\r\n```bash\r\n# create a default configuration file\r\n./bin/lodestar create-config -o my_lodestar_config.toml\r\n# use configuration file in beacon node\r\n./bin/lodestar beacon -c my_lodestar_config.toml\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'm hoping that there may be some libraries available to help unify the different configuration options available, so we won't have to maintain each independently.\r\n",
